---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import bigPicture from '../assets/EmpowerAI-BigPicture.png';
---

<section id="why" class="section why-empower">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-header fade-in">
      <p class="section-label">Why Empower</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built Different. Built for Regulated AI.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Incumbents have distribution and data &mdash; but they don't have the missing middle layer
        that makes AI reliable, governed, and operational in regulated enterprises.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-points fade-in">
        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Model-driven + Agentic + Semantic</h3>
            <p>Deterministic where it must be, probabilistic where it can be. Model-driven codegen + semantic fabric + orchestrated agents.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>"No Hallucination" Posture</h3>
            <p>Evidence, provenance, constraints, and validation are first-class &mdash; not retrofitted as an afterthought.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>The Language LLMs Speak</h3>
            <p>Ontology and semantic modeling aligns with how LLMs reason over structured context &mdash; a compounding advantage in agent reliability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Systems of Action, Not Record</h3>
            <p>Agentic intelligence that turns knowledge into workflow execution &mdash; cross-system, cross-team, cross-domain.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Regulated-First DNA</h3>
            <p>Governed AI, responsible AI, private hosting, air-gap-ready patterns &mdash; built for scrutiny from day one.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-point">
          <div class="why-point-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Vertical AI on a Horizontal Platform</h3>
            <p>Start with flagship apps, then open the platform. The Salesforce/Veeva pattern &mdash; without becoming a services company.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="why-visual fade-in">
        <Image src={bigPicture} alt="Empower AI big picture â€” platform architecture" width={560} quality={80} />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-callout fade-in">
      <div class="callout-label">Positioning</div>
      <blockquote>
        Palantir proved that ontology-driven systems unlock enterprise value &mdash; but deployments are heavy,
        bespoke, and slow. Empower AI delivers the same class of semantic + operational intelligence as a modern,
        AI-native platform: automated semantic fabric, agentic orchestration, and deterministic model-driven
        generation for rapid delivery of vertical AI systems.
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <div class="why-pitch fade-in">
      <p class="section-label">The Pitch</p>
      <p>
        "Empower AI is a horizontal enterprise platform that lets you build vertical AI systems fast &mdash;
        especially in regulated industries. It combines a semantic knowledge fabric that organizes and grounds
        company knowledge with an agentic orchestration layer that turns AI into real workflows and actions.
        On top of that, we use deterministic model-driven generation to produce proven, enterprise-grade
        architecture quickly &mdash; reducing engineering time and token costs. The result is governed, auditable
        AI that can run in private or air-gapped deployments and withstand scrutiny in healthcare, life sciences,
        med device, pharma, and similar environments."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .why-header .section-subtitle {
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .why-points {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .why-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .why-point-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .why-point h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .why-point p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .why-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-8));
  }

  .why-visual img {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .why-callout {
    background: var(--color-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    position: relative;
  }

  .callout-label {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .why-callout blockquote {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .why-pitch {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .why-pitch p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .why-visual {
      position: static;
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
